---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';

const title = `Privacy Policy | ${SITE.name}`;
const description =
  'How Payoff Logic handles your data: calculator inputs stay in your browser, privacy-friendly analytics, and full disclosure of advertising cookies.';
const lastUpdated = 'July 11, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-navy-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-navy-700">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains what information {SITE.name} ("we," "us")
        collects when you visit this website, how we use it, and the choices
        you have. The short version: our calculators run entirely in your
        browser, we never see the numbers you enter, and we collect as little
        as possible.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">1. Calculator inputs</h2>
      <p>
        The values you type into our calculators (loan amounts, interest
        rates, home prices, debts, and so on) are processed locally in your
        browser. They are <strong>not transmitted to, stored on, or logged by
        our servers</strong>. If you use a "share" link, your inputs are
        encoded into the URL itself — only share that link with people you
        trust to see those numbers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">2. Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand aggregate traffic —
        which pages are visited and how the site performs. Cloudflare Web
        Analytics does not use cookies, does not fingerprint devices, and does
        not track you across sites. It shows us anonymous, aggregate counts
        only.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">3. Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        To keep the calculators free, we may display advertising served by
        third-party networks such as Google AdSense. When advertising is
        active on the site:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
        <li>
          Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads
          based on your prior visits to this and other websites.
        </li>
        <li>
          Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to
          serve ads based on your visits to this site and/or other sites on
          the Internet.
        </li>
        <li>
          You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
          <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-navy-900 underline hover:text-navy-600" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>
          or
          <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" class="text-navy-900 underline hover:text-navy-600" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aboutads.info</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Advertisers never receive the values you enter into our calculators.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">4. Information you send us</h2>
      <p>
        If you contact us by email, we receive your email address and the
        contents of your message. We use this only to respond to you, and we do
        not add you to any mailing list or share your address with third
        parties.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The site itself does not set cookies for its core functionality. Any
        cookies present come from the third-party advertising described in
        Section 3 once advertising is active. Most browsers let you block or
        delete cookies in their settings.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">6. Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is directed at a general adult audience and is not intended
        for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
        information from children.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">7. Data security &amp; retention</h2>
      <p>
        Because calculator inputs never leave your browser, there is no
        calculator data for us to secure or retain. Contact emails are kept
        only as long as needed to handle your request.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">8. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        If we change this policy — for example, when advertising goes live —
        we will update this page and the "last updated" date above.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900">9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Reach us via the
        <a href="/contact/" class="text-navy-900 underline hover:text-navy-600">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
